You will need to create the default configuration file:
 ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/minirc.dfl
which can be done by executing 'minicom -s' as root.

Do not forget to change the default 'Serial Device', which can be found in
the 'Serial port setup' section.
===========================================================================
